        "\n",
        "# String Formatting {.unnumbered}\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "You can use the following escape characters:\n",
        "\n",
        "- `\\n`: new line\n",
        "- `\\t`: tab\n",
        "- `\\\\`: backslash\n",
        "- `\\'`: single quote\n",
        "- `\\\"`: double quote\n",
        "- `\\b`: backspace\n",
        "- `\\r`: carriage return\n",
        "- `\\f`: form feed\n",
        "- `\\ooo`: octal value\n",
        "- `\\xhh`: hex value\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "You can use the `+` operator to concatenate strings. <br>\n"
